BlueFocus Communication Group Co., Ltd. Key Developments

BlueFocus Communication Group Co., Ltd. Announces to Implement Final Cash Distribution Plan for 2016, Payable on June 26, 2017
Jun 22 17
BlueFocus Communication Group Co., Ltd. announced 2016 final distribution plan to be implemented. The company announced cash dividend (tax included) of CNY 0.65353100 per 10 A Shares for the year 2016. Record date is 23 June 2017; ex-date is 26 June 2017 and payment date is 26 June 2017.


Bluefocus Communication Group Co., Approves Amendments to Its Articles of Association
May 18 17
BlueFocus Communication Group Co., Ltd. at its annual general meeting held on May 17, 2017 approved amendments to the articles of association of the company.


BlueFocus Communication Group Co., Ltd. Approves Cash Dividend for the Year 2016; Approves Board Changes
May 18 17
BlueFocus Communication Group Co., Ltd. approved cash dividend of CNY 0.65350000 per ten shares (tax included) for the year 2016, considered at its annual general meeting held on May 17, 2017.

At the same meeting, the shareholders of the company approved the appointment of Jiang Xiliang and Zhao Xinge as Non-Independent Directors and Zhu Yunyang as Supervisors of the company.


