Summary for BlueFocus Communication Group Co.,Ltd.
BlueFocus Communication Group Co., Ltd. is a provider of brand management services. The Company operates its businesses principally through brand management services, including brand communications, product promotion, crisis management, activity management, digital media marketing and corporate social responsibility services, among others. The Company's businesses are applied in industries such as high technology, consumer goods, automobile, pharmaceutical, finance, aviation and tourism, education, government and non government-organizations (NGOs), distribution, real estate, energy, as well as entertainment and media, among others. The Company operates its businesses primarily in Beijing, Shanghai, Guangzhou and Shenzhen, China.


